7	🇧🇷 Brazil — Grassroots Cup	🇧🇷 WE'RE GOING TO THE PHILLY GRASSROOTS CUP — BRAZIL TEAM!\n\nLighthouse 1893 SC is proud to sponsor the Brazil team in the 2026 Philly Grassroots Cup — a World Cup-style city tournament representing 12 nations!\n\n🏆 3-game group stage + knockouts · 12 Nations\n📅 First match: June 7, 2026\n📍 Philadelphia, PA\n🥅 Final: June 19 at Drexel Vidas Field\n\nSpots are open to ALL players! Fill out the fill out interest form in bio.\n\n👉 linktr.ee/Lighthouse1893Soccer\n\n#PhillyGrassrootsCup #Brazil #Lighthouse1893 #PhillySoccer #CASASoccer #WorldCup2026 #Lighthouse1893SC #GrassrootsCup	promo_7.jpg	https://footballhome.org/images/posts/promo_7.jpg	draft	\N	2026-05-16 00:14:14.178453+00	17987912096995665	\N	2026-05-16 00:14:01.689149+00	2026-05-16 00:14:14.178453+00	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
