9	⚽ U23 Men's Team	⚽ NOW FORMING: LIGHTHOUSE U23 MEN'S TEAM!\n\nLighthouse 1893 SC is forming a U23 Men's team in partnership with CASA Soccer!\n\n📅 First Match: May 30, 2026\n🏆 League: CASA Soccer · Philadelphia\n📍 Philadelphia, PA\n🎯 Open to ALL players\n\nInterested? Fill out the interest form in bio!\n\n👉 linktr.ee/Lighthouse1893Soccer\n\n#Lighthouse1893 #U23 #PhillySoccer #CASASoccer #U23Soccer #Lighthouse1893SC #PhillyFootball	promo_9.jpg	https://footballhome.org/images/posts/promo_9.jpg	draft	\N	2026-05-16 00:26:50.501208+00	17975296041043705	\N	2026-05-16 00:26:38.047164+00	2026-05-16 00:26:50.501208+00	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
11	Triple-Header Match Day — Sun Jun 7	⚽🏟️ MATCH DAY AT LIGHTHOUSE — STILL TIME TO GET HERE! 🏟️⚽\n\nThree games. One pitch. All day football today (Sunday, June 7) at the Lighthouse Sports & Entertainment Complex.\n\n🔥 All matches are FULL REGULATION — 11v11, 90 minutes.\n\n✅ FINAL — 10:00 AM — Lighthouse Women's Club 2 - 2 Boyertown (Tri-County League)\n🕞 3:15 PM — 🇸🇩 Sudan vs Egypt 🇪🇬 (CASA Grassroots Cup · Group A · Matchday 1)\n🕔 5:15 PM — 🇧🇷 Brazil vs Puerto Rico 🇵🇷 (CASA Grassroots Cup · Group C · Matchday 1)\n\nThe CASA Grassroots Cup group stage kicks off TODAY — come watch the country teams in their opening matches!\n\n✅ FREE Admission\n✅ FREE Gated Parking (onsite)\n✅ Shaded Pitch-Side Seating\n\n📍 Lighthouse Sports & Entertainment Complex\n199 East Erie Avenue, Philadelphia, PA 19140\n\nBring the family. Bring your friends. Bring your flag. See you pitch-side. ⚓️🌎\n\n#Lighthouse1893 #PhillySoccer #CASAGrassrootsCup #TriCountyLeague #WomensSoccer #MatchDay #Lighthouse1893SC #PhillyFootball	promo_11.jpg	https://footballhome.org/images/posts/promo_11.jpg	posted	\N	2026-06-07 17:37:26.126559+00	18092756339579090	\N	2026-06-07 16:52:10.502902+00	2026-06-07 17:37:26.126559+00	MATCH DAY	Triple-Header at Lighthouse	10:00 AM — Lighthouse Women vs Boyertown (Tri-County)\n3:15 PM — Sudan vs Egypt (CASA Grassroots Cup)\n5:15 PM — Brazil vs Puerto Rico (CASA Grassroots Cup)	Free Admission · Free Parking · Shaded Pitch-Side Seating	lighthouse:br,casa:bl,tcwsl:tl	\N	\N
12	Lighthouse Youth Soccer — Now Enrolling	⚽ LIGHTHOUSE YOUTH SOCCER — NOW ENROLLING\n\nOpen to all boys & girls entering 1st through 6th grade.\nTravel & In-House Leagues.\n\nSummer training + fall season · all skill levels welcome.\n\n📍 Lighthouse Sports & Entertainment Complex\n199 East Erie Avenue, Philadelphia, PA 19140\n\n#Lighthouse1893 #PhillySoccer #YouthSoccer	promo_12.jpg	https://footballhome.org/images/posts/promo_12.jpg	draft	\N	\N	\N	\N	2026-06-08 16:33:31.99206+00	2026-06-08 21:45:18.990114+00	YOUTH SOCCER	Boys & Girls · Ages 6–13	U6–U8 · Foundations\nU9–U11 · Development\nU12–U13 · Competitive	Real Pitch · Real Coaches · Real Community	lighthouse:br	\N	\N
